CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773936670
OL,3,CNottingham attacks detective
OL,4,Capologises to families for not taking
OL,5,Chair sample
OL,7,FExtending the apology to the parents
OL,8,Fof Barnaby and Grace, Mr Sanders
OL,9,Fdescribed them as individuals who had
OL,10,F"very eloquently" raised their
OL,11,Fconcerns.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@QO]
